eNCA spoke to Former world champion, Mzuvukile ‘Old Bones’ Magwaza for more. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Former world champion, Mzuvukile ‘Old Bones’ Magwaza is ready to resurrect his career. Magwaza was shot and left for dead in January 2018. The former WBF, IBF Intercontinental and WBA International bantamweight champion plans to return to the ring for his first professional fight in four years. eNCA spoke to Magwaza. Watch the video above.